OL,6,FThe mother of a teenage boy who tried
OL,7,Fto take his own life after he was
OL,8,Ftricked into performing sex acts
OL,9,Fonline has warned of the "devastating"
OL,10,Fimpact of social media grooming.
OL,12,FBen - not his real name - was 14 when
OL,13,Fhe exchanged messages with what he
OL,14,Fthought was a girl of a similar age.
OL,16,FIt was only after corresponding for a
OL,17,Fnumber of weeks that he discovered he
OL,18,Fwas talking to a man, who then used
OL,19,Fthreats and blackmail to coerce him
OL,20,Finto sending sexual images and
OL,21,Fperforming sex acts live on Skype.
