OL,6,FThe material was shared with five
OL,7,Fother men who then bombarded Ben with
OL,8,Ffurther demands.
OL,10,FBen, from Yorkshire, complied for two
OL,11,Fyears before he started having panic
OL,12,Fattacks and attempted to take his own
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,FHis mother said she knew nothing of
OL,16,Fthe abuse until police turned up at
OL,17,Fher door after arresting the
OL,18,Fperpetrator.
