OL,6,F"I've never asked Ben about exactly
OL,7,Fwhat happened because he doesn't want
OL,8,Fto talk about it", she said.
OL,10,F"But I do know he got to know things
OL,11,Fabout his family, where they work and
OL,12,Fthen when Ben said he'd had enough,
OL,13,Fthat he wasn't interested, the
OL,14,Fblackmail started. The demands just
OL,15,Fgot bigger...he said he'd kill Ben's
OL,16,Ffamily if he didn't do as he was told."
OL,18,FThe abuser was later given a nine-year
OL,19,Fextended prison sentence.
