OL,6,FThe charity said Snapchat was the most
OL,7,Fcommon platform used by perpetrators
OL,8,Fto target children online last year,
OL,9,Fwith the messaging app cited in almost
OL,10,Fhalf of grooming cases across the UK.
OL,12,FWhatsApp, Facebook and Instagram were
OL,13,Falso used.
OL,15,FNSPCC chief executive Sir Peter
OL,16,FWanless said: "One year since the
OL,17,FOnline Safety Act became law and we
OL,18,Fare still waiting for tech companies
OL,19,Fto make their platforms safe for
OL,20,Fchildren.
